{"tid":1896501,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"睇飛機文發現,支那有隻郵輪年廿六上船,用一日驗船, 之後放走所有人","createTime":"2020-02-25T07:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T08:21:59.000Z","uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6628d4c8cdc23c86a492cfc04302b46ef4c7ad","tid":1896501,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"1月20日， &ldquo;歌詩達賽琳娜號&rdquo;郵輪滿載3706名遊客和1100名船員，從天津出發。<br />\n1月23日，郵輪停靠日本佐世保港。船上15人出現發熱症狀，其中包括2名兒童和10位外籍船員。<br />\n1月24日，&ldquo;歌詩達賽琳娜號&rdquo;郵輪返回天津。<br />\n1月25日淩晨6點30分，大陸衛生署登上&ldquo;歌詩達賽琳娜號&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n=== TLDR ===<br />\n發現船上有148名湖北仔<br />\n26名有去過武漢<br />\n抽17份樣本驗, 陰性<br />\n=== TLDR ===<br />\n<br />\n15時30分 批准下船<br />\n1月26日零時15分，天津官方宣佈，&ldquo;歌詩達賽琳娜號&rdquo;郵輪應急處置工作全部結束<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支那用左一日就放晒D人走, 零確確診</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機文大陸link就不貼<br />\nkeyword: 歌詩達賽琳娜號/ Costa Serena"},{"pid":"d13645e575ccfd416840850aa65d2dcc3a663680","tid":1896501,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"推，密切留意"},{"pid":"f1423d816435db9e43e5fe879f9b4782e6c7842b","tid":1896501,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"Costa Serena被佢地用來比較鑽石公主號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打撚晒飛機"},{"pid":"1fea376fdbe228f3226d80137380aebef8480159","tid":1896501,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:52:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7472f1d3bde87f9ce8826a73934d2cd37d0cd4f2","tid":1896501,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim